[{"id":"1960175ad05dc10b1760dde9a61078a5","from":"Stotter, Manuela","from_email":"MStotter@Related.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"RE: catch up","date":"2008-01-14T18:27:49.000Z","formatted_date":"Jan 14, 2008","formatted_time":"6:27 PM","body":"I will be in Barcelona next w-e from Friday to Monday.....but if something\nchanges, I will give you a call and you can tell if we can meet.\n\nThansk\n\n \n\nManuela E. St\u00f6tter\n\nRELATED\n\n60 Columbus Circle\n\nNew York, NY 10023\n\nTel: 212.801.3796\n\nCell: 917.498.5285\n\nFax: 212.801.3727\n\nwww.related.com\n\n \n\n  _____  \n\nFrom: J. Epstein [mailto:jeeproject@yahoo.com] \nSent: Monday, January 14, 2008 12:03 PM\nTo: Stotter, Manuela\nSubject: Re: catch up\n\n \n\nI won'tbe back intil friday\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: \"Stotter, Manuela\" <MStotter@Related.com>\nTo: jeeproject@yahoo.com\nSent: Monday, January 14, 2008 11:03:09 AM\nSubject: catch up\n\nHallo Jeffrey,\n\n \n\nI'm sorry I missed you last week. I really hoped to see you and catch up a\nbit. I know you are quite busy and my schedule is not as flexible any more.\n\nI may just stop by at your office to say HI to everybody, but I really wanted\nto see you. I always feel that at the end you were the only person who\nbelieved in me and gave me the opportunity to come to NYC.\n\nMy life changed very much and now I'm very stable and happy. I would not be\nwhere I'm without your initial support.\n\nWell, that's all. THANKS was the only thing I came to say to you.\n\n \n\nLet me know if you ever want to see me and I can stop at 9th 71st street .\n\n \n\nHave a good day, wherever you are today,\n\n \n\nM\n\n \n\nManuela E. St\u00f6tter\n\nRELATED\n\n60 Columbus Circle\n\nNew York, NY 10023\n\nTel: 212.801.3796\n\nCell: 917.498.5285\n\nFax: 212.801.3727\n\nwww.related.com <http://www.related.com/> \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n","body_html":"<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTE